OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJapan outrage as child     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsterilisations revealed    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Two nine-year-olds were among the      
OL,6, 25,000 people forcibly sterilised in   
OL,7, Japan under its post-World War Two     
OL,8, eugenics law, a parliament report has  
OL,9, revealed.                              
OL,11,FThe law, in place for 48 years, forced 
OL,12,Fpeople to undergo operations to prevent
OL,13,Fthem having children deemed "inferior".
OL,15,FMany of them had physical or cognitive 
OL,16,Fdisabilities, or mental illness.       
OL,18,FThe law is widely recognised as a dark 
OL,19,Fchapter in Japan's post-war recovery   
OL,20,Fand was repealed in 1996.              
